title: HOUR 1- Mike Florio Sep 30, 2020
itunes:title: HOUR 1- Mike Florio Sep 30, 2020
description:
Mike Florio tells Dan what the consequences would be for the Falcons to move Matt Ryan. Mike says he doesn't know who would take Matt Ryan right now. Mike says to Dan that the Falcons have done a good job tanking with Matt Ryan.
